Description:
   Cloak:drain is the Necromancer's signature remort cloak. It wraps the
   caster in a dark, life-siphoning aura. When struck in melee combat, there
   is a 35% chance that the cloak will activate, draining hit points from the
   attacker equal to the caster's pseudo-level. The caster is healed for half
   of the drained amount, up to their maximum hit points.

   The cloak does a small amount of damage, but its primary value is the
   lifedrain effect -- sustaining the Necromancer through prolonged fights.
   The attacker's hit points cannot be drained below 10.

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
